Enum Mode

java.lang.Object

      za.sabob.olive.Mode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Mode>
public enum Mode
extends Enum<Mode>

Provides the different modes to run an Olive instance with.

In PRODUCTION mode SQL files and parsed SQL strings will be cached for fast retrieval.

* In DEVELOPMENT mode SQL files will not be cached and can be dynamically updated.

In TRACE mode mode SQL files will not be cached and fine grained logging will be enabled to allow tracing and debugging of the runtime, eg if there are missing named parameters.
